nodes.text: The Alsakan Overlook was the name given to the outcropping on the south side of Mount Tessef, a mountain in the Juran Mountains on the planet Alderaan. From the Overlook, one could see the river that bordered the Alsakan Lowlands to the west, and the Killik-infested southern valley of King's Pass.
The Alsakan Overlook appears as a location on Alderaan in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
